text: the tabernacle itself, and the cover thereof, the hanging that is drawn before the doors of the tabernacle of the covenant, and the curtains of the court, the hanging also that is hanged in the entry of the court of the tabernacle, and whatsoever belongingeth to the right of the altar, the cords of the tabernacle, and all the furniture thereof.
